Gary L. Castagna, CPA

Age : 56Public asset : 1,639,753 USDLinked companies :  Minerals Technologies Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Gary L. Castagna, CPA, is Group President-Performance Materials at Minerals Technologies, Inc. and a Managing Director at Performance Materials Corp.He is on the Board of Directors at Amcol Minerals Europe Ltd. Mr. Castagna was previously employed as Chief Operating Officer & Executive Vice President by AMCOL International Corp., President by Chemdal International Corp., a Managing Director by Chemdal Ltd., and Internal Audit Manager by American Colloid Co.He also served on the board at M-Wave, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Lake Superior State University.



